text: hello my name is Aaron Hennessy the

the AWS toolkit for visual studio the

to create edit and deploy cloud
formation templates all within Microsoft
Visual Studio the included Json editor
is also integrated with Visual Studio to
provide Json parsing with a visual cue
of parsing
errors color highlighting of invalid
keys for a given type intellisense
integration for inline documentation and
easy object
creation
brace

checking intrinsic function help

valid values for the get at and rep

lists with fold identifiers named for
the type or description fields of your
maps for easy identification of folds
here's a quick demonstration of common
operations in the AWS cloud formation
editor for visual studio creating a new
template editing a

stack monitoring stack
progress downloading and editing

stack updating a
stack
